        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1434907694" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1535803135983879014">Hemingway is an acquired taste. Reading his works is like a box of chocolates. You never know what you are going to get. I liked the taste of this one. Although, I was skeptical for the first 400 pages. For me, the best part of the book came in the last 70 pages and took forever to come and I was richly rewarded. The result was satisfying.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


