      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/2252079-for-whom-the-bell-tolls">Quotes from For Whom the Bell...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
